                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "We had orders about you. Reroute around, do not engage, do not confirm the face. The face from the memo with the black bar over the name."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "You keep undoing our sites and now you are at our survey. I am paid to log samples, not to be right about who you are. State your business."
                        }
