                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The officer logged you and ran. I run the sampling bot. The assessment is my job and my job is filed, verified, and none of your concern."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "You came all the way out here to argue with a sample drum. Ruin the numbers, then - if you can get past me."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Survey Crew - the sample run",
                    Label: "foreman_ready"
                },
